S.FORM: == sanmaca == u siwkay nu nipaluma pasubana i cacudadan a lacul u cudad a ngangan: tabernaemontana subglobosa merr. u sapamat a ngangan: apocynaceae u Amilika a ngangan: crape jasmine, crape gardenia, pinwheel flower u zuma a cidekay a kamu Pangcha: x Tayan: x Sejek: x Paywan: x Taluku: x Yuwatan: takiludun huhudan tasasikis tu lisav Rukay: x Cou: nangira siparipe Kabalan: x Kanakanabu: x Laaluwa: x Saysia: x Puyuma: Saw: x Tau: rapanbaka u sulit nu zuma a kamu u sulit nu Hulam 山馬茶 sanmacha u sulit nu Lipun u sulit nu Amilika saungay misapayu' a cidekay Yuwatan, Sakizaya, Cou, Tau u zuma a cidekay cay katineng mukan atu musapayu' tina nipaluma

== sanmaca == o siwkay no nipaloma pasobana i cacodadan a lacol o codad a ngangan: tabernaemontana sobglobosa merr. o sapamat a ngangan: apocynaceae o Amilika a ngangan: crape jasmine, crape gardenia, pinwheel flower o zoma a cidekay a kamo Pangcha: x Tayan: x Sejek: x Paywan: x Taloko: x Yowatan: takilodon hohodan tasasikis to lisav Rokay: x Coo: nangira siparipe Kabalan: x Kanakanabo: x Laalowa: x Saysia: x Poyoma: Saw: x Tao: rapanbaka o solit no zoma a kamo o solit no Holam 山馬茶 sanmacha o solit no Lipon o solit no Amilika saongay misapayo' a cidekay Yowatan, Sakizaya, Coo, Tao o zoma a cidekay cay katineng mokan ato mosapayo' tina nipaloma
